blish command (AR-022).\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775867518480,\"end\":1775867518480}}}\n  Line 11: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775867518571,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2860ce4d3ffexYkB1hNwUAcFPJ\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79f3de15001j1W2DNINmSojTv\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79f34c8f001P7aw1KJ1LCN3Bc\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2860ce4d3ffexYkB1hNwUAcFPJ\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-d7baa25bcc8f4c65bd27bab8552eb8c6\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"error\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# Delta Specification: CLI Publish Command (AR-022)\\n\\n## Module: cmd/cli\\n## Language: Python\\n## Size: L\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Requirement: Publish command options and defaults\\n\\n### Scenario: Publish with all default options\\n- **GIVEN** the user runs `kubectl-agentcube publish`\\n- **WHEN** the command executes\\n- **THEN** the CLI SHALL use default values: `workspace` = `\\\".\\\"`, `version` = `None`, `image_url` = `None`, `image_username` = `None`, `image_password` = `None`, `description` = `None`, `region` = `None`, `cloud_provider` = `None`, `provider` = `\\\"agentcube\\\"`, `node_port` = `None`, `replicas` = `None`, `namespace` = `None`, `verbose` = `False`\\n\\n### Scenario: Publish with custom workspace\\n- **GIVEN** the user runs `kubectl-agentcube publish -f /path/to/workspace`\\n- **WHEN** the command executes\\n- **THEN** the CLI SHALL use `/path/to/workspace` as the workspace path\\n\\n### Scenario: Publish with custom version\\n- **GIVEN** the user runs `kubectl-agentcube publish --version v1.2.3`\\n- **WHEN** the command executes\\n- **THEN** the CLI SHALL use `v1.2.3` as the version string\\n\\n### Scenario: Publish with custom provider\\n- **GIVEN** the user runs `kubectl-agentcube publish --provider k8s`\\n- **WHEN** the command executes\\n- **THEN** the CLI SHALL use `k8s` as the provider instead of default `agentcube`\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Requirement: AgentCube provider prerequisites validation\\n\\n### Scenario: AgentCube provider missing router_url\\n