e script mapping |\\n19: | `agentcube/__init__.py` | Package version `__version__`, exports `app`, runtimes |\\n20: | `agentcube/cli/__init__.py` | CLI subpackage marker |\\n21: | `agentcube/cli/main.py` | Typer `app`, all commands, `_handle_error`, `version_callback` |\\n22: | `agentcube/models/pack_models.py` | `MetadataOptions` dataclass |\\n23: | `agentcube/runtime/__init__.py` | Re-exports runtimes + `MetadataOptions` |\\n24: | `agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py` | `PackRuntime` |\\n25: | `agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py` | `BuildRuntime` |\\n26: | `agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py` | `PublishRuntime` |\\n27: | `agentcube/runtime/invoke_runtime.py` | `InvokeRuntime` |\\n28: | `agentcube/runtime/status_runtime.py` | `StatusRuntime` |\\n29: | `agentcube/services/__init__.py` | Services package docstring |\\n30: | `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` | `AgentMetadata`, `MetadataService`...\n  Line 7: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775867340578,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2860fd53cffeIZwy9rcWI6qt9T\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79f05a10001nCaIGUNVgGgb98\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79f036c6001XK0ia0JAqo8vsb\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2860fd53cffeIZwy9rcWI6qt9T\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I'll create a proposal.md for the CLI publish command implementation based on the specs provided.\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775867340575,\"end\":1775867340575}}}\n  Line 8: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775867340616,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2860fd53cffeIZwy9rcWI6qt9T\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79f12723001VjD8WG8rvJJxIw\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79f036c6001XK0ia0JAqo8vsb\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2860fd53cffeIZwy9rcWI6qt9T\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-92035b9b766444b5906eb9144d9b53df\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"error\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# Proposal: CLI Publish Command Implementation\\n\\n## Overview\\n\\n**AR:** AR-022 — CLI publish command  \\n**Module:** cmd/cli  \\n**Language:** Python  \\n**Size:** L\\n\\nThis proposal outlines the implementation of the `publish` command for the AgentCube CLI tool, which enables publishing/deploying AI agents to either AgentCube (via AgentRuntime CR) or standard Kubernetes (via Deployment + NodePort Service).\\n\\n## Background\\n\\nThe AgentCube CLI (`kubectl-agentcube`) is a developer tool for managing AI agent lifecycle operations including packaging, building, publishing, invoking, and status checking. The `publish` command is a critical component that handles the deployment phase, supporting multiple deployment targets and image preparation strategies.\\n\\n## Requirements\\n\\nBased on the CLI toolkit specification, the publish command must:\\n\\n### Functional Requirements\\n\\n1. **Dual Provider Support**\\n   - Support `agentcube` provider (AgentRuntime CR deployment)\\n   - Support `k8s` provider (standard Deployment + Service deployment)\\n\\n2. **Image Preparation**\\n   - Local build mode: Use Docker push to registry\\n   - Cloud build mode: Use cloud-provided image URL\\n   - Support registry authentication (username/password)\\n\\n3. **Publishing Workflow**\\n   - Validate workspace and metadata\\n   - Prepare container image (push or use provided URL)\\n   - Deploy to Kubernetes (either AgentRuntime CR or standard K8s resources)\\n   - Update metadata with deployment information\\n   - Provide rich console output with progress indicators\\n\\n4. **Configuration Options**\\n   - Version specification (semantic versioning)\\n   - Image ...\n  Line 14: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775867462263,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2860fd53cffeIZwy9rcWI6qt9T\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79f301050019OGP47GiJVR9Fu\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79f12f81001rCedTpkDq5vQ02\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2860fd53cffeIZwy9rcWI6qt9T\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-1aa2f94e3797426c943c1924a988f147\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# AR-022: CLI publish 命令\\n\\n## Overview\\n\\n实现 AgentCube CLI 的 `publish` 命令，用于将构建好的容器镜像发布到 Kubernetes 集群。该命令支持两种发布方式：AgentCube 自定义资源（AgentRuntime CR）和标准 Kubernetes 资源（Deployment + Service），能够处理镜像推送、资源部署和元数据更新。\\n\\n## Purpose\\n\\n提供 `kubectl-agentcube publish` 命令，实现：\\n\\n1. **镜像准备**：支持本地镜像推送到容器注册表，或使用云端构建的镜像 URL\\n2. **AgentCube 提供商**：部署到 AgentRuntime 自定义资源，集成工作负载管理器和路由器\\n3. **标准 K8s 提供商**：部署到标准的 Deployment 和 NodePort Service\\n4. **版本管理**：支持语义化版本号，更新元数据中的部署信息\\n5. **部署配置**：支持命名空间、副本数、节点端口等配置\\n6. **状态验证**：等待部署就绪，提供详细的部署状态反馈\\n\\n## Module\\n\\n`cmd/cli` - AgentCube CLI 工具包\\n\\n## Language\\n\\nPython 3.10+\\n\\n## Size\\n\\nL\\n\\n## Scope\\n\\n### In Scope\\n\\n1. **PublishRuntime 类实现** (`agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py`)\\n   - `publish()` 主方法，支持两种提供商\\n   - `_publish_cr_to_k8s()` - AgentRuntime CR 部署\\n   - `_publish_k8s()` - 标准 K8s 资源部署\\n   - `_prepare_image_for_publishing()` - 镜像准备\\n   - `_prepare_local_image()` - 本地镜像推送\\n   - `_prepare_cloud_image()` - 云端镜像验证\\n   - `_update_publish_metadata()` - 更新发布元数据\\n\\n2. **CLI 命令集成** (`agentcube/cli/main.py`)\\n   - `publish()` Typer 命令函数\\n   - 命令行参数：`--workspace`, `--version`, `--image-url`, `--provider`, `--namespace`, `--replicas`, `--node-port`, `--region`, `--cloud-provider`, `--description`, `--verbose`\\n   - 错误处理和用户反馈\\n\\n3. **AgentCube 提供商** (`agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py`)\\n   - `deploy_agent_runtime()` - 部署 AgentRuntime CR\\n   - 设置默认会话超时\\n   - 配置工作负载管理器和路由器 URL\\n\\n4. **Kubernetes 提供商** (`agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py`)\\n   - `deploy_agent()` - 部署 Deployment 和 Service\\n   - `wait_for_deployment_ready()` - 等待部署就绪\\n   - 支持节点端口配置\\n\\n5. **Docker 服务集成** (`agentcube/service...\n  Line 17: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775867466429,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2860fd53cffeIZwy9rcWI6qt9T\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79f31027001Rq5thGj4S4uNuV\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79f302c6001hwqo4FKCv8uO51\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2860fd53cffeIZwy9rcWI6qt9T\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Created proposal.md for AR-022 (CLI publish command) with comprehensive implementation plan covering dual provider support (AgentCu