QZ8\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79e99fff00166pYDeEEWDB4dG\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28617e7d2ffe87RJQv7ZvCA3ub\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The `design.md` file already contains comprehensive technical implementation details for the AgentCube project. It includes:\\n\\n1. **AR-021** - CLI Build Command (complete design)\\n2. **AR-019** - CLI Binary Entry Points (4 binaries: agentd, picod, router, workload-manager)\\n3. **AR-022** - CLI Publish Command (specifications)\\n4. **Section 10** - Client-Go Library (Kubernetes client for AgentRuntime CRD)\\n5. **Section 11** - Python SDK Design (CodeInterpreterClient, AgentRuntimeClient)\\n6. **Section 12** - Python SDK Specification (detailed requirements)\\n7. **AR-024** - DockerService封装\\n8. **AR-025** - MetadataService与数据模型\\n\\nThe document covers all major components from the `.sdd_prompt.md`:\\n- Package structures\\n- Class/function signatures  \\n- API contracts\\n- Data models (AgentMetadata, MetadataOptions)\\n- Error handling patterns\\n- Testing strategies\\n- Dependencies\\n\\nThe design is already complete at **2871 lines** with all technical implementation details. Is there a specific section you'd like me to expand or modify?\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775866857601,\"end\":1775866857601}}}\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z_logs/AR-026_ST-2.log:\n  Line 10: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775866699908,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28618f847ffeO2FZgDArMKgtuE\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79e75f69001h4fxyvadDPJq4a\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79e73d10001OwArPGbeVsDL7F\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28618f847ffeO2FZgDArMKgtuE\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"glob\",\"callID\":\"toolu_88fa14111ce740409a238a04\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"pattern\":\"**/delta-spec.md\"},\"output\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-026/delta-spec.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cl