stry\n77: - [ ] Verify method uses authentication if provided\n78: - [ ] Verify method returns pushed image URL\n79: - [ ] Verify comprehensive error handling and logging\n80: \n81: **Verification**: Create test workspace with local image and verify image is pushed successfully\n82: \n83: ---\n84: \n85: ### Task 6: Verify _prepare_cloud_image method\n86: - [ ] Verify method gets cloud_provider from options or metadata\n87: - [ ] Verify method raises ValueError if cloud_provider is missing\n88: - [ ] Verify method calls cloud provider API (or raises NotImplementedError)\n89: - [ ] Verify method returns image URL from cloud provider\n90: - [ ] Verify error handling for cloud API failures\n91: \n92: **Verification**: Review implementation and verify appropriate error messages\n93: \n94: ---\n95: \n96: ### Task 7: Verify _publish_cr_to_k8s method (AgentCube provider)\n97: - [ ] Verify method validates router_url is present\n98: - [ ] Verify method validates workload_manager_url is present\n99: - [ ] Verify method gets namespace from options or defaults to \"default\"\n100: - [ ] Verify method creates AgentCubeProvider instance\n\n(Showing lines 1-100 of 1344. Use offset=101 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-022 — CLI publish 命令 Implementation Tasks\n\n**Module**: `cmd/cli`\n**Language**: Python\n**Size**: L\n**Design Stage**: ST-3 Completed\n\n## Task Breakdown\n\n### Task 1: Verify publish command interface in main.py\n- [ ] Verify publish command exists in agentcube/cli/main.py\n- [ ] Verify all required parameters are defined:\n  - [ ] workspace (default \".\", short flag \"-f\")\n  - [ ] version (optional)\n  - [ ] image_url (optional)\n  - [ ] image_username (optional)\n  - [ ] image_password (optional)\n  - [ ] description (optional)\n  - [ ] region (optional)\n  - [ ] cloud_provider (optional)","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-022/tasks.md","time":{"sta